Package com.interpss.core.dclf.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DclfAlgorithmImpl
    DclfAlgo --> AclfNet --> DclfSolver --> AclfNet - DclfAlgo has two ref objects (AclfNet and DclfSolver).
    DclfFactoryImpl
    An implementation of the model Factory.
    DclfPackageImpl
    An implementation of the model Package.
    DclfSolver
    Solver for dclf and sensitivity analysis injBus |--- monitoring branch ---| withdrawBus - Sensitivity is regarding to an injection bus or an injection bus + a withdraw bus - Branch shifting factor for a monitoring branch is the ratio of the monitoring branch current with regarding the the injection current + withdraw current
    DcLoadflowImpl
    An implementation of the model object 'Dc Loadflow'.
    MultiOutageLODFHelper
    a helper class for calculating multiple Open/Close outage LODF, per outage branches defined in the Dclf algo object
    SenAnalysisBusImpl
    An implementation of the model object 'Sen Analysis Bus'.
